Stadium Ticket Flask RESTful API for GNU/Hurd, GNU/Linux, and Unix.

This project has been tested with Python 3.6 and 3.7 on the following
platforms:

+============+==================+===============================+
| OS Family  | OS Distribution  | OS Versions (OS Ports)        |
+============+==================+===============================+
| GNU/Cygwin | MS Windows (NT)  | 10 (x86_64)                   |
+------------+------------------+-------------------------------+
| GNU/Hurd   | Debian           | 10 (i686)                     |
+------------+------------------+-------------------------------+
| GNU/Linux  | CentOS           | 7 (x86_64)                    |
+------------+------------------+-------------------------------+
| GNU/Linux  | Debian           | 10 (amd64, s390x)             |
+------------+------------------+-------------------------------+
| GNU/Linux  | Fedora           | 30 (x86_64)                   |
+------------+------------------+-------------------------------+
| GNU/Linux  | Kali             | 2019 (amd64)                  |
+------------+------------------+-------------------------------+
| GNU/Linux  | KDE Neon         | 5.16 (amd64)                  |
+------------+------------------+-------------------------------+
| GNU/Linux  | Linux Mint       | 19.2 (amd64)                  |
+------------+------------------+-------------------------------+
| GNU/Linux  | openSUSE         | Leap 15.1 (aarch64, x86_64)   |
+------------+------------------+-------------------------------+
| GNU/Linux  | openSUSE         | Tumbleweed 20190916 (x86_64)  |
+------------+------------------+-------------------------------+
| GNU/Linux  | Oracle Linux     | 7.7 (x86_64)                  |
+------------+------------------+-------------------------------+
| GNU/Linux  | Raspbian         | 10 (armhf)                    |
+------------+------------------+-------------------------------+
| GNU/Linux  | Ubuntu           | 18.04 LTS (amd64)             |
+------------+------------------+-------------------------------+
| GNU/Linux  | Ubuntu           | 19.04 (amd64)                 |
+------------+------------------+-------------------------------+
| Unix       | Apple macOS      | 10.14 (x86_64)                |
+------------+------------------+-------------------------------+
| Unix       | FreeBSD          | 11.3 (amd64)                  |
+------------+------------------+-------------------------------+
| Unix       | FreeBSD          | 12.0 (amd64)                  |
+------------+------------------+-------------------------------+
| Unix       | NetBSD           | 8.1 (amd64)                   |
+------------+------------------+-------------------------------+
| Unix       | OpenIndiana      | Hipster 2019.04 (x86_64)      |
+------------+------------------+-------------------------------+

